OL,6,FOfficers from the National Crime
OL,7,FAgency's Operation Stovewood - an
OL,8,Finvestigation into historic
OL,9,Fallegations of sexual abuse in the
OL,10,Ftown - found that King began abusing
OL,11,Fthe first victim in the summer of
OL,12,F2008, with his girlfriend at the time,
OL,13,FLouise Tye.
OL,15,FTye, who died last year, knew the girl
OL,16,Fthrough her father.
OL,18,FShe forced the girl to have sex with
OL,19,Fher and King and King paid her for her
OL,20,Frole in the abuse.
