OL,6,FOn one occasion the girl was
OL,7,Faccompanied by her best friend, aged
OL,8,Faround 13 or 14 at the time. King
OL,9,Fabused them together.
OL,11,FThe first victim escaped later moved
OL,12,Fhome, but King tracked her down and in
OL,13,F2010 raped her at her new address.
OL,15,FKing, who had no previous criminal
OL,16,Fconvictions, came to the NCA's
OL,17,Fattention when Operation Stovewood
OL,18,Fofficers identified the first girl as
OL,19,Fa potential victim of child sexual
OL,20,Fabuse in late 2018.
