OL,6,FSpecially trained officers spoke with
OL,7,Fher and over time she detailed what
OL,8,FKing had done to her and her friend.
OL,10,FKing and Tye were arrested in 2021.
OL,12,FTye, 41, of Kimberworth, was charged
OL,13,Fwith inciting a child to engage in
OL,14,Fsexual activity but died in 2023.
OL,16,FKing stood trial at Sheffield Crown
OL,17,FCourt and was found guilty of 17
OL,18,Fcharges including rape, attempted rape
OL,19,Fand engaging in sexual activity with a
OL,20,Fchild.
