OL,6,FSenior investigating officer Stuart
OL,7,FCobb said: "This case demonstrates
OL,8,Fthat it's never too late to report
OL,9,Fsexual offences, so I urge anyone who
OL,10,Fwas abused as a child to tell police."
OL,12,FSamantha Thompson, of the Crown
OL,13,FProsecution Service, said: "Neil King
OL,14,Ftargeted his young victims with money,
OL,15,Falcohol, drugs and gifts, grooming
OL,16,Fthem for child sexual abuse, including
OL,17,Frape and attempted rape.
